{"content":"<header data-hk=\"1.85\" class=\"shadow-md sm:p-2 w-full bg-white dark:text-white dark:bg-navy mb-20\"><div data-hk=\"1.86\" class=\"flex justify-between\"><a data-hk=\"1.87\" class=\"justify-self-start self-center m-3 ml-5 text-md sm:text-2xl\" href=\"en-US/\">Perseus</a><div data-hk=\"1.88\" class=\"xs:hidden m-3 mr-5 tham tham-e-spin tham-w-6 \"><div data-hk=\"1.89\" class=\"tham-box\"><div data-hk=\"1.90\" class=\"dark:bg-white tham-inner\"></div></div></div><nav data-hk=\"1.91\" class=\"hidden xs:flex\"><ul data-hk=\"1.92\" class=\"mr-5 flex\"><li data-hk=\"2.0\" class=\"m-3 p-1\"><a data-hk=\"2.1\" href=\"en-US/docs\" class=\"px-2\">Docs</a></li><li data-hk=\"2.2\" class=\"m-3 p-1\"><a data-hk=\"2.3\" href=\"en-US/comparisons\" class=\"px-2\">Comparisons</a></li><li data-hk=\"2.4\" class=\"m-3 p-1\"><a data-hk=\"2.5\" href=\"en-US/plugins\" class=\"px-2\">Plugins</a></li></ul></nav></div><nav data-hk=\"1.93\" id=\"mobile_nav_menu\" class=\"xs:hidden w-full text-center justify-center hidden\"><ul data-hk=\"1.94\" class=\"mr-5\"><li data-hk=\"3.0\" class=\"m-3 p-1\"><a data-hk=\"3.1\" href=\"en-US/docs\" class=\"px-2\">Docs</a></li><li data-hk=\"3.2\" class=\"m-3 p-1\"><a data-hk=\"3.3\" href=\"en-US/comparisons\" class=\"px-2\">Comparisons</a></li><li data-hk=\"3.4\" class=\"m-3 p-1\"><a data-hk=\"3.5\" href=\"en-US/plugins\" class=\"px-2\">Plugins</a></li></ul></nav></header><div data-hk=\"1.95\" class=\"overflow-y-scroll\"><main data-hk=\"1.96\" class=\"h-full\"><div data-hk=\"1.0\" class=\"bg-cover h-full flex justify-center items-center text-center dark:text-white\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;.perseus/static/svg/splash_page_bg.svg&quot;), url(&quot;.perseus/static/svg/polygon_scatter.svg&quot;);\"><div data-hk=\"1.1\"><p data-hk=\"1.2\" class=\"text-7xl xs:text-8xl sm:text-9xl p-2 font-extrabold\">Perseus</p><p data-hk=\"1.3\" class=\"text-lg\">The Rust framework for the modern web.</p><br data-hk=\"1.4\"/><div data-hk=\"1.5\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center\"><a data-hk=\"1.6\" class=\"py-3 px-4 m-2 font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-2xl text-white bg-indigo-500 hover:bg-indigo-400 transition-colors duration-200\" href=\"en-US/docs\">Get Started</a><a data-hk=\"1.7\" class=\"inline-flex items-center py-2 px-4 m-2 font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-2xl dark:text-white ring-4 ring-indigo-500 hover:ring-indigo-400 transition-all duration-200\" href=\"https://github.com/arctic-hen7/perseus\"><span data-hk=\"1.8\" class=\"mr-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 17 16\" fill=\"none\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\"><g clip-path=\"url(githublogo)\" class=\"jsx-120409797\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.18391.249268C3.82241.249268.253906 3.81777.253906 8.17927c0 3.46933 2.279874 6.44313 5.451874 7.53353.3965.0991.49563-.1983.49563-.3965v-1.3878c-2.18075.4956-2.67638-.9912-2.67638-.9912-.3965-.8922-.89212-1.1895-.89212-1.1895-.69388-.4957.09912-.4957.09912-.4957.793.0992 1.1895.793 1.1895.793.69388 1.2887 1.88338.8922 2.27988.6939.09912-.4956.29737-.8921.49562-1.0904-1.78425-.1982-3.5685-.8921-3.5685-3.96496 0-.89212.29738-1.586.793-2.08162-.09912-.19825-.3965-.99125.09913-2.08163 0 0 .69387-.19825 2.18075.793.59475-.19825 1.28862-.29737 1.9825-.29737.69387 0 1.38775.09912 1.98249.29737 1.4869-.99125 2.1808-.793 2.1808-.793.3965 1.09038.1982 1.88338.0991 2.08163.4956.59475.793 1.28862.793 2.08162 0 3.07286-1.8834 3.66766-3.66764 3.86586.29737.3965.59474.8921.59474 1.586v2.1808c0 .1982.0991.4956.5948.3965 3.172-1.0904 5.4518-4.0642 5.4518-7.53353-.0991-4.3615-3.6676-7.930002-8.02909-7.930002z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" class=\"jsx-120409797\"></path></g><defs class=\"jsx-120409797\"><clipPath id=\"githublogo\" class=\"jsx-120409797\"><path fill=\"transparent\" d=\"M0 0h15.86v15.86H0z\" transform=\"translate(.253906 .0493164)\"></path></clipPath></defs></svg></span><span data-hk=\"1.9\"> GitHub</span></a></div></div></div><div data-hk=\"1.10\" class=\"bg-cover py-4 text-white\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;.perseus/static/svg/stacked_waves.svg&quot;);\"><div data-hk=\"1.11\" class=\"flex justify-center text-center text-lg w-full\"><p data-hk=\"1.12\" class=\"p-1 xs:p-4 max-w-7xl\">Perseus is a web development framework built entirely in Rust, designed to empower efficient development of the next generation of lightning-fast sites for the modern web. It comes with server-side rendering, static site generation, internationalization, and inferred routing built-in, letting you build even the most complex sites in a breeze.</p></div><br data-hk=\"1.13\"/><div data-hk=\"1.14\" class=\"flex justify-center\"><ul data-hk=\"1.15\" class=\"text-center max-w-7xl mx-2\"><li data-hk=\"1.16\" class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div data-hk=\"1.17\" class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p data-hk=\"1.18\" class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Static generation</p><p data-hk=\"1.19\" class=\"text-gray-100\">Pre-render pages at build-time before you've even had any visits!</p></div></li><li data-hk=\"1.20\" class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div data-hk=\"1.21\" class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p data-hk=\"1.22\" class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Server-side rendering</p><p data-hk=\"1.23\" class=\"text-gray-100\">Render pages on the server to reduce the load on the client.</p></div></li><li data-hk=\"1.24\" class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div data-hk=\"1.25\" class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p data-hk=\"1.26\" class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Internationalization</p><p data-hk=\"1.27\" class=\"text-gray-100\">Out-of-the-box support for building your app in multiple languages.</p></div></li><li data-hk=\"1.28\" class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div data-hk=\"1.29\" class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p data-hk=\"1.30\" class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Incremental generation</p><p data-hk=\"1.31\" class=\"text-gray-100\">Render pages on-demand and cache them for future use.</p></div></li><li data-hk=\"1.32\" class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div data-hk=\"1.33\" class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p data-hk=\"1.34\" class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Revalidation</p><p data-hk=\"1.35\" class=\"text-gray-100\">Rebuild pages automatically without lifting a finger.</p></div></li><li data-hk=\"1.36\" class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div data-hk=\"1.37\" class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p data-hk=\"1.38\" class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">CLI</p><p data-hk=\"1.39\" class=\"text-gray-100\">Comes with a friendly interface to accelerate your development pace.</p></div></li><li data-hk=\"1.40\" class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div data-hk=\"1.41\" class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p data-hk=\"1.42\" class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Inferred routing</p><p data-hk=\"1.43\" class=\"text-gray-100\">You do your app, Perseus does the rest automatically.</p></div></li><li data-hk=\"1.44\" class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div data-hk=\"1.45\" class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p data-hk=\"1.46\" class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">App shell</p><p data-hk=\"1.47\" class=\"text-gray-100\">Get all the benefits of a single-page app without any of the downsides.</p></div></li><li data-hk=\"1.48\" class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div data-hk=\"1.49\" class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p data-hk=\"1.50\" class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Single-command deployment</p><p data-hk=\"1.51\" class=\"text-gray-100\">Take your apps to production with one command.</p></div></li><li data-hk=\"1.52\" class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div data-hk=\"1.53\" class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p data-hk=\"1.54\" class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Static exporting</p><p data-hk=\"1.55\" class=\"text-gray-100\">Deploy your apps without needing a server.</p></div></li></ul></div><br data-hk=\"1.56\"/><br data-hk=\"1.57\"/><div data-hk=\"1.58\" class=\"flex justify-center text-center text-lg w-full p-1 xs:p-4\"><div data-hk=\"1.59\" class=\"p-4 shadow-2xl rounded-xl max-w-lg\"><p data-hk=\"1.60\" class=\"underline text-2xl mb-2\">Building a Perseus App:</p><ol data-hk=\"1.61\" class=\"list-decimal list-inside\"><li data-hk=\"1.62\"><span data-hk=\"1.63\"><!--#-->Install Perseus:<!--/--> <code data-hk=\"1.64\">cargo install perseus-cli</code></span></li><li data-hk=\"1.65\"><span data-hk=\"1.66\">Build your awesome app with <a href=\"https://github.com/sycamore-rs/sycamore\" class=\"underline\">Sycamore</a></span></li><li data-hk=\"1.67\"><span data-hk=\"1.68\"><!--#-->Serve your app locally:<!--/--> <code data-hk=\"1.69\">perseus serve</code></span></li><li data-hk=\"1.70\"><span data-hk=\"1.71\"><!--#-->Deploy your app to a single directory:<!--/--> <code data-hk=\"1.72\">perseus deploy</code></span></li><li data-hk=\"1.73\"><span data-hk=\"1.74\">Upload that to a server!</span></li></ol></div></div></div><div data-hk=\"1.75\" class=\"pb-24 flex flex-col justify-center text-white\" style=\"background: url(&quot;.perseus/static/svg/cta_bg.svg&quot;);background-size:cover;\"><div data-hk=\"1.76\" class=\"text-3xl 2xs:text-4xl xs:text-5xl sm:text-6xl p-2 font-extrabold text-center\"><p data-hk=\"1.77\">What are you waiting for?</p><p data-hk=\"1.78\">Dive in and start building for the web of tomorrow!</p></div><br data-hk=\"1.79\"/><div data-hk=\"1.80\" class=\"flex justify-center\"><a data-hk=\"1.81\" class=\"py-3 px-4 m-2 text-xl font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-2xl text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-500 transition-colors duration-200\" href=\"en-US/docs\">Get Started</a></div><br data-hk=\"1.82\"/><div data-hk=\"1.83\" class=\"flex justify-center\"><a data-hk=\"1.84\" class=\"py-2 px-4 m-2 font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-2xl text-white bg-indigo-500 hover:bg-indigo-400 transition-colors duration-200\" href=\"en-US/comparisons\">Or See How Perseus Compares</a></div></div></main></div><footer data-hk=\"1.97\" class=\"w-full flex justify-center py-5 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-navy-deep\"><p data-hk=\"1.98\" class=\"dark:text-white mx-5 text-center\"><span data-hk=\"1.99\">© <a href=\"https://github.com/arctic-hen7\" class=\"underline\">arctic-hen7</a> ⁨2021⁩, see license <a href=\"https://github.com/arctic-hen7/perseus/blob/main/LICENSE\" class=\"underline\">here</a>.</span></p></footer>","state":null,"head":"<title>Perseus</title>"}